com.joffrey_bion.csv_epoch_synchronizer.k4b2

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joffrey_bion.csv_epoch_synchronizer.k4b2.Sample

  • public class Sample
extends Object
    Contains the statistics on the breathing of the user over a short period of time. These values are contained in one line in the K4b2 file.
    Author:
    Joffrey BION
